{"tid":1167450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那外交部亮劍】美國軍方稱兩艘美軍軍艦通過台灣海峽","createTime":"2019-05-23T04:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T05:22:09.000Z","uid":173631,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa281d0830a6e0475fea10b4bebfc628a671923","tid":1167450,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"（原標題：快訊！兩艘美軍軍艦穿越台灣海峽）<br />\n據路透社剛剛消息，美國軍方發言人聲稱，兩艘美國海軍軍艦5月22日穿越台灣海峽。<br />\n美軍軍艦最近一次穿越台灣海峽在4月28日。針對美艦穿越台海舉動，中國外交部發言人耿爽4月29日表示，台灣問題是中美關系中最重要最敏感的問題。我們敦促美方恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，慎重妥善處理涉台問題，以免對中美關系和台海和平穩定造成消極影響。<br />\n<a href=\"http://comment.tie.163.com/EFRSNP0J0001899O.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcomment.tie.163.com%2FEFRSNP0J0001899O.html&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=106ecf95\" target=\"_blank\">http://comment.tie.163.com/EFRSNP0J0001899O.html</a>"},{"pid":"40c0f041a3b4da0a972adb9c5a88362854c57646","tid":1167450,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d21a787e478e7197f49d35fe8e9ab6be6378ea","tid":1167450,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"口交部又嘈"},{"pid":"84042930a7193a252f5fcb37335e08c406d80d02","tid":1167450,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"美國講撚左， 大家一個中国理解唔同<br />\n同埋支那唔係最興 變哂歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bfc454579a2a823233f347e529711e821234be","tid":1167450,"uid":18955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"40c0f041a3b4da0a972adb9c5a88362854c57646","tid":1167450,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n帶路之前打包